Global Antifouling Paint and Coating Market Insights
Antifouling Paint and Coating Market size was valued at USD 4.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 7.2 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Antifouling Paint and Coating Market Overview
The global antifouling paint and coating market was valued at USD 12.5 billion in 2024 and is expected to grow at a CAGR of 6.3% from 2025 to 2032. This market growth is driven by the increasing demand for advanced marine coatings and the need to improve the operational efficiency of vessels by preventing the growth of marine organisms on ship surfaces. The antifouling coatings are designed to prevent biofouling, which can increase fuel consumption, reduce speed, and accelerate corrosion. As the shipping industry continues to grow globally, the demand for these paints is expected to rise across various sectors such as shipping, offshore oil and gas, and marine recreational boats.

